name: Domestic
description:
✨Domestic Collectors✨
Domestic Collectors is a web and soon to be app based play to earn game where you can play, socialize and earn real money through being domestic. Earn by receiving $DMC from the reward pool or level up and trade your workers.

Connect your wallet and receive your free Domestor! Go to work for Domestic points. Use your points to upgrade your workers or save them for weekly rewards in $DMC.

The vision of Domestic Collectors is to keep developing the platform making profits grow consistently for active and devoted players.

BECOME A DOMESTOR TODAY!
